Abstract: We suggest how to redefine the multicointegration model of Granger
  	and Lee (1990) in terms of an I(2) system and subsequently propose a
  	one-step procedure for estimation and inference which will have
  	favourable statistical properties compared to the two-step procedure
  	suggested by Granger and Lee. With respect to the single equation
  	residual based cointegration procedure for I(2) systems we tabulate
  	new critical values that are necessary to accomodate the presence of
  	deterministic components.
Classification-JEL: C12; C13; C22
Keywords: Cointegration, multicointegration, I(2) processes
