Title: Modelling the Relationship between Government Policy, Economic
  	Growth, and Deforestation in the Brazilian Amazon.
Author-Name: Lykke Eg Andersen
Author-Email: landersen@eco.aau.dk
Author-WorkPlace-Name: University of Aarhus, Denmark, Department of
